frames.caption: Under the luminous full moon, a towering spectral figure looms over a bridge where three cloaked figures stand, holding glowing staffs. The scene is set in a mystical landscape with rocky cliffs and a distant castle, creating an atmosphere of enchantment and mystery.
frames.description: The scene depicts a fantasy setting with a giant spectral figure in a hooded cloak, holding a staff and a wand, standing over three smaller cloaked figures on a bridge. The background features a full moon, rocky cliffs, and a castle, suggesting a magical and otherworldly environment.

frames.caption: In a mystical, moonlit landscape, three robed figures stand on a bridge, holding glowing staffs. They face a towering spectral figure with a skeletal face, who holds a staff and dagger, illuminated by the full moon behind.
frames.description: The scene is set in a dark, fantastical landscape under a full moon. Three figures in robes stand on a bridge, confronting a large, ghostly apparition. The atmosphere is eerie and magical, with an air of mystery and tension.

summary: People: cloaked figures, robed figures. Objects: staff, bridge, wand, castle, dagger. Nature: moon, trees, cliffs, clouds, mountains. Actions: standing, holding, confronting. Emotions: mystery, enchantment, mystical, eerie. Scenes: fantasy, night, nighttime. Concepts: magic, supernatural
